<s> I am still not convinced that this is a good idea.  </s>
<s> As far as I know, none of the major HTML browsers today will cope very well with an SGML declaration in a document, let alone a link process definition.  </s>
<s> Presumably !USELINK... would become legal within an HTML document.  </s>
