<s> If you want to have the ICADD attributes in a separate file, assume that the SGML 97 rule has passed to allow !AttList X a "b" #IMPLIED percy (x|y|z) "x" !AttList X c "d" #FIXED so that you can put all the #FIXED attributes (and maybe others) in a separate file and include it from the base DTD.  </s>
